{"pr_number": 1295, "pr_title": "RDM-10671: increased HTTP max header size to address issue reported i\u2026", "pr_createdAt": "2020-12-30T09:58:37Z", "pr_url": "https://github.com/hmcts/ccd-data-store-api/pull/1295", "timeline": [{"oid": "95a68865275402fd88bf02b8d5ee3b9e15a499fd", "url": "https://github.com/hmcts/ccd-data-store-api/commit/95a68865275402fd88bf02b8d5ee3b9e15a499fd", "message": "RDM-10671: increased HTTP max header size to address issue reported in RDM-10274", "committedDate": "2020-12-30T09:57:59Z", "type": "commit"}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDU1MTI0MzY5MQ==", "url": "https://github.com/hmcts/ccd-data-store-api/pull/1295#discussion_r551243691", "bodyText": "A flux change has set this to 100KB on demo, already, for fixing an issue on case sharing. (under RDM-10571)\nI think, it's better to either change the default value here to 100KB or raise an additional flux change like that one below.\nhttps://github.com/hmcts/cnp-flux-config/pull/7414/files", "author": "MSancaktutar", "createdAt": "2021-01-04T10:49:35Z", "path": "src/main/resources/application.properties", "diffHunk": "@@ -4,6 +4,7 @@ server.servlet.contextPath=\n server.compression.enabled=true\n server.compression.mime-types=application/json,application/xml,text/html,text/xml,text/plain\n server.error.include-message=always\n+server.max-http-header-size=${MAX_HTTP_HEADER_SIZE:24KB}", "originalCommit": "95a68865275402fd88bf02b8d5ee3b9e15a499fd", "replyToReviewId": null, "replies": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDU1MTI0NTI2Mw==", "url": "https://github.com/hmcts/ccd-data-store-api/pull/1295#discussion_r551245263", "bodyText": "Also, since \"SERVER_MAX_HTTP_HEADER_SIZE\" itself is also as good as \"MAX_HTTP_HEADER_SIZE\", we may refrain from introducing a new env var like this. Setting \"SERVER_MAX_HTTP_HEADER_SIZE\" in any environment will make it anyway... If we still want to introduce \"MAX_HTTP_HEADER_SIZE\", we will need to change the demo flux var for consistency.", "author": "MSancaktutar", "createdAt": "2021-01-04T10:52:39Z", "replyToReviewId": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDU1MTI0MzY5MQ=="}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDU1MTI3Mzk5MA==", "url": "https://github.com/hmcts/ccd-data-store-api/pull/1295#discussion_r551273990", "bodyText": "ok it makes sense. I'll just set it to 100KB, get rid of the custom env var, since we can use SERVER_MAX_HTTP_HEADER_SIZE in the future if we need to increase more", "author": "mario-paniccia", "createdAt": "2021-01-04T11:56:06Z", "replyToReviewId": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDU1MTI0MzY5MQ=="}], "type": "inlineReview"}, {"oid": "b3a17b5a65ba19920abf4f4838b7832ee4509b72", "url": "https://github.com/hmcts/ccd-data-store-api/commit/b3a17b5a65ba19920abf4f4838b7832ee4509b72", "message": "RDM-10671: increased HTTP max header size to address issue reported in RDM-10274", "committedDate": "2021-01-04T11:57:15Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "998916880df55ae88ea8ee1010f5513aeb5aa5a6", "url": "https://github.com/hmcts/ccd-data-store-api/commit/998916880df55ae88ea8ee1010f5513aeb5aa5a6", "message": "cve supressions", "committedDate": "2021-01-04T13:25:37Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "7b9994662169a5cd2ceb86235dc2c70a5e0347b4", "url": "https://github.com/hmcts/ccd-data-store-api/commit/7b9994662169a5cd2ceb86235dc2c70a5e0347b4", "message": "supress cve", "committedDate": "2021-01-05T09:15:23Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "935420c8be05e60e6590dc1f67183763ef9ac2e0", "url": "https://github.com/hmcts/ccd-data-store-api/commit/935420c8be05e60e6590dc1f67183763ef9ac2e0", "message": "fix ordering in tests", "committedDate": "2021-01-06T14:04:45Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "aed0320e7646e55fac0cd880e3afe7a2d6ca5acb", "url": "https://github.com/hmcts/ccd-data-store-api/commit/aed0320e7646e55fac0cd880e3afe7a2d6ca5acb", "message": "fixes", "committedDate": "2021-01-06T16:01:41Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "11523ff62990b768d254067d47ebf5ca7a5ef414", "url": "https://github.com